 Controversial Nigerian actress, Nkechi Blessing has issued a warning to fans and colleagues who criticize her or try to tell her how she should spend her life. Taking to her Instagram page, Nkechi Blessing shared a photo of the car and her holding the car key. According to Nkechi Blessing, the company’s CEO had sent the car gift urging her to manage it till she gets a bigger car but noted that the vehicle isn’t small. Nkechi Blessing added that she’s honestly short of words and prayed that God would embarrass the company owner with blessings noting that he is indeed heavy sent. She wrote: “Got home from this omoluabiholdings. He said pls manage this all car till you are able to get a bigger car, hos is this small? I am short of words honestly…But God will embarrass you with blessings. You are indeed heaven sent. Thankful is never enuf”. See post below: 